Hi Doug.

I do not exactly know what you mean with &quot;scale for arrow foll palette&quot;, but you can try to change the line
&lt;pre class=&quot;prettyprint&quot;&gt;
unset colorbox
&lt;/pre&gt;
to
&lt;pre class=&quot;prettyprint&quot;&gt;
set colorbox
&lt;/pre&gt;

This will add a colorbox to your figure (have a look at this &lt;a href=&quot;./../../default-color-map/&quot;/index.html rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;example&lt;/a&gt;) showing the scale used for the color of the arrows.
